    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Rocks, material, or objects that produces a magnetic field external to itself, which causes the magnet to attract other ferromagnetic materials, such as iron, and attracts or repels other magnets.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
